        <td height="20" align="left" valign="top" class="textalign">We strongly recommend that  you and all members of your party are covered by a policy of travel insurance.  Adequate travel insurance is essential. It is your responsibility to ensure  that the insurance cover you purchase is suitable and adequate for your  particular needs. All insurance premiums are payable in full at the point of sale and are  sold incorporating a 14 day cooling off period after which time some policies  may be non-refundable and you should check at the time of purchase. The 14 day  cooling off period only applies if you have not departed the UK or made any  claim under the insurance policy. If you choose to travel without adequate  insurance cover, we will not be liable for any losses howsoever arising, in  respect of which insurance cover would otherwise have been available.</td>
