        <td height="20" align="left" valign="top" class="textalign"><p>You must telephone us or the airline at least 72 hours before the  departure time shown on your ticket to confirm that there has been no changes.  This applies to both outbound and return flights. We will not be liable for any  additional costs due to your failure to reconfirm flights. Reconfirming your  flight at least 72 hours before departure is a minimum requirement.<strong> </strong></p>        </tr>
